bropals.lib.simplegame.math

Class Vector2DCapped

  • java.lang.Object
    • bropals.lib.simplegame.math.Vector2D
      • bropals.lib.simplegame.math.Vector2DCapped

  • public class Vector2DCapped
extends Vector2D
    A Vector2D that is similar to a normal Vector2D only has maximum values. These maximum values apply for both the positive and negative directions.
